moa stone
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:(usually pl.) a round stone, one of many found in groups or masses, and reputed to be a moa gizzard or crop stone.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
